      "writtenOn": "2017-10-06T23:01:51Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Sorry, not sure what you mean. This should result in a list saying \"verify for {linux-amd64, win-amd64}\", and both platforms would be verified for both packages. This mirrors how the manifest would be treated on both of those respective platforms.\n\nVerification isn\u0027t interpreted relative to other packages; it\u0027s an independent accumulating directive that\u0027s applied to the entire manifest, just like manifest evaluation is.",
